1. Imam *susan* nos danas. (I have a *stuffy* nose today.)
2. *Susan* je bio miris u vazduhu. (There was a *burnt* smell in the air.)
3. Moramo da *susimo* veš pre nego što padne kiša. (We have to *dry* the laundry before it starts raining.)
4. Ona je *susila* kosu fenom. (She was *blow-drying* her hair.)
5. Kada je stigla kući, primetila je *suvu* travu na dvorištu. (When she got home, she noticed *dry* grass in the yard.)
6. Kada god jedeš *suvo* voće, pij dovoljno vode. (Whenever you eat *dried* fruit, drink enough water.)
7. *Susnice* su bile punjene sirom i pečurkama. (The *pastry puffs* were filled with cheese and mushrooms.)
8. Molim te, *susnežice* mi daj u kesi. (Please, give me the *hard candies* in the bag.)
9. On je *susretljiv* čovek i uvek će pomoći drugima. (He is a *kind* person and will always help others.)
10. Čekam *susret* sa svojom najboljom drugaricom. (I'm waiting for a *meeting* with my best friend.)